[quote=“jc22493, post:6, topic:269040”][quote author=Surfr link=topic=355078.msg2718781#msg2718781 date=1237834109]

You can’t declare methods inside of other methods.

So how would I fix this

Would I have to take the entire method and put it else where in my client class?

If so, how do I know where it starts or finishes? Its really confusing.
[/quote]
Instead of declaring it in another method, just find where the former method ends, then add the new one.[/quote]

I’m not sure i understand “new one”? and how do i find out where it ends thats what i’m asking, how can you tell?
